org.forgerock.openam.core.rest.session

Class SessionResourceV2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.core.rest.session.SessionResourceV2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.forgerock.json.resource.CollectionResourceProvider

    public class SessionResourceV2
extends Object
implements org.forgerock.json.resource.CollectionResourceProvider
    End point for querying the session info via a REST interface. Currently describe three different query entry points for this Resource, useful when querying Session Information:
    • All - All sessions across all servers known to OpenAM.
    • [server-id] - Lists the sessions for that server instance.
    • [session-id] - Details opf the session information
    This resources acts as a read only resource.
